Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.49,0:00:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.64,0:00:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:01:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Unknown Challenger:\N The Giant Mobile Fortress Submerges!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Dark Games that occurred last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did Bakura-{\i0}kun{\i1} really lose like Malik said...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So {\i0}you{\i1} came here, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where did you send Bakura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who knows?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody {\i0}knows{\i1} where those who lose a Dark Game are sent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So how should {\i0}I{\i1} know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the man who acted as Malik's shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} also got hurt because of Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know what happened between him and my other self relating to his lost memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I just can't forgive Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened? An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot that I'm on an aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two dreaming about huddled together like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell was that for...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up! Something's wrong with the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu-{\i1}san{\i0}! When did {\i1}she{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Steady the ship already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Battle Ship went off the route of our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and turn us back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...! It's just... The auto-driving system changed route by itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about? Then manually override it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this ship okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel you... I {\i1}feel{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind of evil intent...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like something really {\i1}entertaining{\i0} is about to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't change it to Manual Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost control!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:04:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alcatraz's computer also refused access!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no signal from the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the destination of our final battles, Alcatraz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the location of the Finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}pitiful wreckage{\i0} is a symbol of the founder of Kaiba Corporation, Gozaburo Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our foster father, Gozaburo Kaiba,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attempted to conquer the world using the great military industry he founded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These ruins are a symbol of his dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After he died, my big brother changed Kaiba Corporation into a gaming industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He destroyed the former military facilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he then built the Duel Tower in their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I built the Duel Tower deliberately in the ruins of Alcatraz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a symbol of my determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment I receive the title of Duel King at the top,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll gain true victory for the first time in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'll finally be freed of his abominable curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1} seems to hate his father....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what happened between them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured out the cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hacker invaded our computer and gained access to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is controlling the system, and it\Nseems he wants to steer the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must land on Alcatraz on schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's going {\i1}on{\i0} here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You trying to kill us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really no way to override the control?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're completely under the hacker's control!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How's this possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it Gozaburo's ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He doesn't want us landing on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are {\i1}you{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you telling me it was this child...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been waiting for you, Seto...\N And I welcome you Duelists as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He addressed Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1} so formerly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that kid looks kind of like him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He looks exactly like my brother used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me! I asked you who you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:07:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I had to put it in simple terms, Seto, I'd say I am a person far greater than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now shall we get to the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little punk... You sure like to hear yourself talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now then, I would like to invite you to be my guests in my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah... What in the world are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the {\i1}hell{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's monstrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure what's going on, but things are getting quite amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying! We've lost complete control of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in their command now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I-I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could this Noah brat be capable of doing all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can I ask you to get off the ship, Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course, the other Duelists, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I were to... refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm afraid you all have become my prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's after {\i1}me{\i0}. This has nothing to do with {\i1}you guys{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, what are your intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe I told you before that I was inviting {\i0}all{\i1} the Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that we should do what he wants for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, this isn't only your problem anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like he's going to let us go that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:10:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\N-Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't need anyone else but them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You two will remain on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's mistaken us for Duelists...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka, you should stay on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't let you risk your life alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The atmosphere here is {\i1}filled{\i0} with chaos and destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just stay back and observe for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To be honest, there are some people here who have been eagerly waiting to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're just a bit up ahead.\N They'll explain everything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so dark we can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's someone here, come out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto Kaiba and your little friends...\N It's been {\i1}quite{\i0} some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}can't{\i0} be! You guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}can't{\i0} be! You guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Big Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The Big 5?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys {\i1}know{\i0} them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They betrayed Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}. They were the group that controlled Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They used cheap tricks to try and take over my big brother's company!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't they lose in the game they set up themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And weren't they unable to return to our world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}President...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why don't you play a little game with us, gambling on your firing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, you aren't {\i0}qualified{\i1} to be our president!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Disappear along with the Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unforgivable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll pay, Big Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master of Dragon Knight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Galaxy Crusher!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is impossible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Upon returning to the real world, they never regained consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wandered the Virtual World for ages after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a world where you eventually lose all sense of who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing driving us is the {\i1}anger{\i0} and need for {\i1}revenge{\i0} against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only one who we hate, Seto Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other people who {\i1}also{\i0} got in the way of our plans and caused our suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi Mutou and his pack of buddies are just as guilty for shaming us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That grudge isn't even {\i1}justified{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as persistent as you always were, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you fools come back, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we roamed the world of cyberspace,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone who understood our feelings gave us a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I presume you mean that little brat we met earlier called Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah-{\i1}sama{\i0} gave us but one condition to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we still want to control Kaiba Corporation as the Big Five,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have to Duel you all and beat you fairly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to Duel us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though we want to kill you all as soon as possible, we can't disobey Noah-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:15:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to get out of here safe and sound, the only way is to Duel with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're gonna Duel, there's no way I'm gonna lose to you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, we invite you to be our guests in the Duel World.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we in a jungle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Virtual Space, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. No matter how scary it looks, it's all just an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not just the colors and shapes... Even the smells seem real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.61,0:15:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can even imitate pulses in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I told you... It's an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Threatening me with such childish holograms that can't even project the sense of touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, this is nothing more than a poor monkey-level copy of the Solid Vision {\i1}I{\i0} created.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys {\i1}kidding{\i0} here, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our Duels are based on the Deck Master System.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deck Master System?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll present a simulated system Duel so you can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Total Defense Shogun will act as his own Deck Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And we'll set Blue-Eyes White Dragon as\N Seto Kaiba's Deck Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blue-Eyes is the Deck Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of rule is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! I'll Summon Lord of Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll activate the Magic Card,\NDragon-Calling Flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll use its Special Effect to Summon two other Dragon-Types to the field from my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, I'll Summon my Deck Master to the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he Summoned three\N Blue-Eyes at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So the Deck Master can be placed on the field as a separate Summon from a Normal Summon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, a Fusion Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And thanks to its Deck Master Ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Ultimate Dragon can attack on the same turn it was Fusion Summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon!\N Direct Attack Total Defense Shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But because Total Defense Shogun is a Deck Master himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he can pay the cost of 1000 Life Points to activate his Deck Master Ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Total Defense Barrier!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Due to the Effect of Total Defense Barrier, the attacking Monster is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the Deck Master is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}regardless of how many Life Points the player has, he loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Any Monster chosen to be the Deck Master has an additional Special Ability to its usual ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Monster you choose to be your Deck Master becomes one of the main points to your strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screwing with us like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you said we'd be Dueling fairly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why did you make up such ridiculous rules?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Five, I won't go easy on you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept the Duel with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any other way out of here if you don't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all...! You're not giving us a choice at {\i1}all{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll take your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Betting my pride as a Duelist on the line, I swear to win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... I'll be sure to protect you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Good luck, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to accept the Duel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count me in! I'll give you a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's get em, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute. But what'll happen to us if we lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bring up an {\i1}excellent{\i0} point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:21:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural that the victorious party is to be presented with compensation from the losing party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As per the risk of your losing to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our minds wandering this Cyber World will enter your bodies and take control of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scumbags...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you'll be {\i1}exchanged{\i0} with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll wander the Cyber World for {\i1}all eternity{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! That's low!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our {\i1}revenge{\i0} against you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(133,144)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Big Five, who didn't learn their lesson, show up before us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they want to have a Duel with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're told, "You can't go back\Nif you don't accept",
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no choice but accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a different Virtual Space, separate from before,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the first coming before Yugi is The Deepsea Warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Deck Master System is to allow the Big Five to take the forms of Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Deck Master - Deepsea Warrior"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.05,0:22:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise